quiz.question:

def example(L):
	''' (list) -> list
	'''
	i = 0
	result = []
	while i < len(L):
		result.append(L[i])
		i = i + 3
	return result

options.a: Return a list containing every third item from L starting at index 0

options.c: Return a list containing every third index from L starting at index 0

options.d: Return a list containing the items from L starting from index 0, omitting every third item
